title: Health/Fitness club companies - Fitness First UK revenue 2012 to 2015
summary: The chart at hand is a line chart where the x axis denotes Year and a y axis denotes Revenue in million U.S. dollars. In total the number of data points it has is 4.
Overall Revenue in million U.S. dollars has decreased over the Year.
Revenue in million U.S. dollars is slightly decreasing from 2012 to 2015.
The steepest decrease occurs in between the Year 2014 and 2015.
The highest Revenue in million U.S. dollars, of value 919.98 was reached at Year 2012
Minimum Revenue in million U.S. dollars about 676.52 was reached at Year 2015
